milestones.description: New Zealand's 211-run win against U.S.A. is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 206-run win against Australia
Nathan Astle has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (88) in an innings in ODIs for NZ, going past Nathan Astle's 84
